1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,680
Nifuza kukwereka uko wakora ubushakashatsi ku kintu icyo ari cyo cyose kuko ubushakashatsi ari imbaraga.

2
00:00:05,680 --> 00:00:10,000
Nanone kandi, ni ubuhanga, kandi iyo umaze kumenya uko ubikora, ushobora kwigiraho.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:11,000
icyo ushaka cyose.

4
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:14,760
Kandi uramutse umenye ko muri iyi minsi abantu benshi batazi gukora ubushakashatsi, bazi uko

5
00:00:14,760 --> 00:00:15,760
kugira ngo ushakishe.

6
00:00:15,760 --> 00:00:19,880
Kandi mu by'ukuri hari itandukaniro rikomeye cyane kuko iyo ushakishije, uba wishingikirije ku bandi

7
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:22,440
abantu bagutekerezeho kandi ibyo si byo twifuza.

8
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:23,840
Twifuza gukora neza kurushaho.

9
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:26,080
Bityo rero, ubushakashatsi bufite ibipimo.

10
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:29,560
Sisitemu nkoresha ifite ine, reka mbikwereke.

11
00:00:29,560 --> 00:00:31,680
Icya mbere ni ugushakisha ku butaka.

12
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:35,600
Aha ni ho ugomba gutangirira, ariko ni na ho abantu benshi bahagarara.

13
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:41,760
Ibi ni byo ushakisha kuri Google, amashusho ya TikTok, ibisobanuro bya YouTube, ibisubizo bya AI.

14
00:00:41,760 --> 00:00:46,519
Kandi ikibazo cyo guhagarara hano ni uko urimo gufata imyanzuro ihindagurika

15
00:00:46,519 --> 00:00:48,640
ntibasobanukirwe uko byubatse.

16
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:49,640
Reka dufate urugero.

17
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:55,000
Reka tuvuge ko ushakisha ibijyanye n'ibinyabuzima by'umwijima maze ugasanga hari ibijyanye n'ibinyabuzima by'umwijima

18
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:57,600
ni 85% by'isanzure ry'ikirere.

19
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,760
Ntitubibona.

20
00:00:58,760 --> 00:01:00,520
Ibyo bigira ingaruka ku mbaraga z'ikiremwamuntu.

21
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:05,120
Uzi ibyo bintu byose, ariko n'ubu ntusobanukiwe ibintu nk'ibyo.

22
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:11,440
cyangwa se ni ikihe gihamya gifatika gihamya ko ibyo ari ukuri cyangwa se ni iyihe nyigisho zihanganye na byo?

23
00:01:11,440 --> 00:01:13,480
None se, ni gute umuntu ashyira mu cyiciro cya mbere neza?

24
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:17,400
Uyakoresha kugira ngo wigishe aho gukoresha kugira ngo wigishe.

25
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:23,560
Ku bw'ibyo, intego yawe muri iki cyiciro yagombye kuba iyo kwiga amagambo, ugasobanukirwa ibitekerezo by'ingenzi

26
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:27,760
no gushaka ibindi bibazo, ugasobanukirwa ibyo utaramenya

27
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,920
icyo ukiri gushishikazwa n'ukuri.

28
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:34,800
Wamara iminota iri hagati ya 10 na 15 ushakisha ku rwego rwa mbere.

29
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:39,000
Hanyuma, uhagarara maze ukibaza uti "ni iki ntasobanukiwe?"

30
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:42,160
Kandi icyo kibazo ni urugi rwawe rwo kugera ku rwego rwa kabiri.

31
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:44,760
Icyiciro cya kabiri ni ugukwirakwiza isoko.

32
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:47,160
Aha ni ho utangira gukora iperereza.

33
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,760
None se ibi birasa bite?

34
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:51,880
Ibyo ni ugusuzuma imirongo n'ingingo.

35
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:55,520
Ni ugusoma ibitabo by'ubushakashatsi byose aho gusoma mu magambo make gusa ibitabo by'ubushakashatsi.

36
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:59,120
Urimo gukurikirana imyirondoro n'ibisobanuro n'ibisobanuro.

37
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,520
Aha ni ho uzajya.

38
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:01,520
Ibyo ni ibiki?

39
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:03,520
Ibyo byaturutse he?

40
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:05,680
Reka dusubire ku rugero rw'ibinyabuzima by'umwijima.

41
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:08,640
Ubu ntukigera ukoresha Google cyangwa TikTok.

42
00:02:08,640 --> 00:02:10,759
Ugiye gufungura urubuga rwa NASA.

43
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:12,640
Urimo ugena ku bushakashatsi bwatanzwe.

44
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:18,520
Urimo gutangiza icyigisho cy'igihindagurika cy'imiterere y'ibice by'inyenyeri, kandi urimo kubona ibyo abantu babonye

45
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,520
abahanga mu bya siyansi.

46
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:24,400
Ibyo rero ni iby'ingenzi cyane kuko ubu ubona ibimenyetso aho kubona gusa imyanzuro.

47
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:28,080
None se wakora iki kugira ngo ufungure neza ibintu byose?

48
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,640
Ntugasome gusa iyo paji maze uyishyiremo.

49
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:33,600
Ugomba kuba ufite amakarita atanu cyangwa icumi y'ibintu byose ureba.

50
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:36,400
Muri iki gihe, wagombye gukurikiza amabwiriza yatanzwe.

51
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:41,760
Ku bw'ibyo, uhereye ku ngingo ukagera ku bushakashatsi ukagera ku makuru y'umwimerere, ibyo byose ni byiza.

52
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,760
hari byinshi bifitanye isano.

53
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:49,760
Ugomba gushyira mu mwanya wa mbere inyandiko za.edu's.gov, zashyizwe ahagaragara, ibikubiyemo byose byatanzwe n'impuguke mu by'ikoranabuhanga

54
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,760
mu isambu.

55
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:56,000
Kandi wagombye kwibaza uti "ni ikihe gitekerezo nshingiyeho?

56
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:59,799
Kubera ko niba udashobora gusubiza icyo kibazo, ushobora kuba ukiri ku rwego rwa mbere.

57
00:02:59,799 --> 00:03:02,959
Ngera ku rwego rwa gatatu, ari rwo kumenya imiterere.

58
00:03:02,959 --> 00:03:07,519
Kandi ntekereza ko iki ari cyo gihe ukuri gutangira kugaragara kuko

59
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:13,040
Muri iki cyiciro, icy'ingenzi ugamije ni ugereranya isoko nyinshi kandi uritayeho

60
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:16,000
ku masezerano n'ibitekerezo bivuguruzanya.

61
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:19,880
Ubona ibitekerezo bikomeje kugaragara.

62
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:25,200
Mu by'ukuri urimo ushakisha ibintu biboneka kenshi muri ayo masoko, yaba

63
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:31,480
ni imibare cyangwa ibibazo cyangwa ibitekerezo cyangwa intiti kuko bigaragaza ko ari iby'ingenzi.

64
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:35,160
Reka tuvuge ko usomye ibintu bitandatu bitandukanye ku birebana n'ibintu by'umwijima.

65
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:39,359
Kandi batandatu muri bo bavuze ko umuzenguruko w'ibice by'inyenyeri udasa n'uw'inyenyeri zigaragara.

66
00:03:39,359 --> 00:03:41,800
Yavuze ko wenda amategeko y'imbaraga rukuruzi ari amakosa.

67
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:46,280
Ubu noneho mu by'ukuri murabona ko ibyo byose bihuje n'icyo kibazo.

68
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:51,240
Iyo ubonye ibipimo by'ibanze, ukabona n'impaka ziriho, ugatangira kubona ibintu by'ukuri

69
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:53,280
gusobanukirwa ibyo wiga.

70
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:56,720
Ku rwego urwo ari rwo rwose, incuro eshatu ni zo zikwiriye.

71
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:59,000
None se, ni iki abantu benshi bemeranyaho?

72
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:01,640
Nawe wagombye kubona ko hari ibyo utemeranyaho.

73
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:05,720
Reka turebe aho abahanga batandukaniye kuri iyo ngingo.

74
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,920
Byaba byiza usuzumye ibimenyetso ubonye.

75
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:11,880
Ushobora gutandukanya ibimenyetso bikomeye n'ibitekerezo.

76
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:17,039
Ushobora no gukora imbaho eshatu z'imitekerereze cyangwa ukazandika niba ubyifuza.

77
00:04:17,039 --> 00:04:22,039
Ariko kimwe muri byo ni amakuru musanga ahuje n'ibisubizo by'ibisubizo byose.

78
00:04:22,039 --> 00:04:27,680
Hariho ubundi bwerekeza ku makuru avugwaho impaka, hakaba n'ubundi bwerekeza ku makuru adafite ishingiro.

79
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:32,020
Kandi ukora ibyo, mu by'ukuri urimo wigisha ubwawe no kubaka ubwenge bwawe.

80
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:33,720
gusuzuma icyo kibazo.

81
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:38,960
Icyiciro cy'ubujyakuzimu n'icy'ingingo kuko aho ni ho uhagarika kwiga amakuru

82
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:41,800
ugatangira gutekereza mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga.

83
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,520
Uribaza ibibazo byiza kurushaho.

84
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:48,400
Urimo wubaka ingero z'imitekerereze y'ikibazo urimo gukora ubushakashatsi maze ugatangira

85
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:52,800
guhuza ibitekerezo mu nzego zitandukanye z'ubushakashatsi.

86
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:58,000
Bityo rero, urimo ushakisha uko ibintu by'icyo uri gukoraho ubushakashatsi bizaba bimeze.

87
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:02,680
Aho kugira ngo twibaze icyo ibintu by'umwijima ari cyo, twibaza ibibazo byimbitse kurushaho.

88
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:08,000
Turibaza ibibazo nk'ibisobanuro by'impamvu imbaraga rukuruzi zikora ibintu muri ubwo buryo cyangwa se ni ibihe byemezo byakozwe

89
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:13,480
mu rugero rwacu rw'ibintu by'umwijima biriho ubu cyangwa icyo ibyo byose bigomba kuba ari ukuri

90
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,480
kugira ngo ukore ikosa.

91
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:20,360
Mu by'ukuri urimo witoza gutekereza mu buryo bwimbitse no kwibaza ibibazo byiza,

92
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:22,360
ni ingenzi cyane mu bushakashatsi.

93
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:27,880
Mu rwego turimo twibaza ibibazo by'icyiciro cya kabiri, ntabwo twibaza gusa iki, ahubwo twibaza impamvu n'impamvu.

94
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:31,160
Byagenda bite se niba twubaka ku ngero zacu zo mu bwenge?

95
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:34,120
Ku bw'ibyo, jya ufata urupapuro ururebere imbere yawe.

96
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:37,120
Ikinyabuzima cy'umwijima, ni cyo gifata umwanya wo kubura imibare.

97
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,000
Ibyo bigaragazwa n'ingaruka z'imbaraga z'imbaraga rukuruzi.

98
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:41,200
Ibyo ntibishobora kubonwa mu buryo butaziguye.

99
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:44,920
Jya uyishyira hanze kugira ngo urebe ikarita yayo maze utangire kuyishyira hamwe.

100
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,080
Ibintu by'umwijima ni ibintu byo mu rwego rwa fiziki.

101
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,240
Ni inyigisho y'ibyaremwe.

102
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,280
Ni filozofiya ya siyansi.

103
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:54,960
Ushobora gufata amakuru ufite ukayashyira mu bimenyetso, mu bintu bidafite ishingiro,

104
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:58,559
ku birebana n'icyo kibazo, ni ukuvuga ko ubumenyi bwacu bufite aho bugarukira.

105
00:05:58,559 --> 00:06:02,599
Iyo utangiye kuyishushanya imbere yawe maze ugakora icyitegererezo utangira kubona

106
00:06:02,599 --> 00:06:06,320
Iyo utekereje ku mishyikirano yose, utangira kubona ko hari icyuho.

107
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:10,159
Kandi biratangaje kubona ukuntu ibyo bigufasha kubisobanukirwa.

108
00:06:10,159 --> 00:06:13,599
Icyo ubushakashatsi buvuga ni uko budafite umurongo, ahubwo bufite umugozi.

109
00:06:13,599 --> 00:06:17,719
Niyo mpamvu ushakisha, hanyuma ukagura, hanyuma ugereranya, hanyuma ukubaka ibyo bintu by'ubwenge

110
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,720
ingero z'abantu.

111
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:21,240
Kandi ibyo bigereranyo byo mu bwenge bituma ubona ibibazo byiza kurushaho.

112
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:25,640
Hanyuma ugasubiramo ibintu byose ukoresheje ibibazo byiza ushakisha

113
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:28,680
ukongera ugasuzuma maze ugakora izindi moderi.

114
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:31,720
Uko ni ko witoza kwitekerezaho.

115
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:34,680
Icyo gihe ni bwo utangira gusobanukirwa ikintu.

116
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:39,000
Ni muri ubwo buryo gukurikirana amatsiko yawe bigira imbaraga nyinshi.

